{
  "id": "adv_bond_hrk_01_03",
  "title": "佐伯遙子3",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふふーん。楽しみだなー！　大学の友達と\nご飯なんて久々だものね……あら、メッセージ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~he. I can't wait! It's been so long\nsince I've had a dinner with my college friends… huh‚ a message?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_message-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7899.999999999999
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11033.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.5333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。来れなくなっちゃったのね……こ、こんな時も\nあるある！　気持ちを切り替えて……あ！　あれは――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. So they couldn't come… t-there are times like\nthis‚ yeah! Getting my mind back… Ah! That's――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333334605,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16566.6665395
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "遙子じゃない。こんな所でどうしたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's Haruko. What's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2000003814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2000003814
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.9666670481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "友達とのご飯の予定が急にリスケになっちゃって\nfranさんもオフ？　どこか行くの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My dinner plans with my friends were suddenly canceled\nIs fran-san off‚ too? Are you going out somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.9666670481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3333337147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。予定は済ませたし、もう帰るけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I've finished my plans‚ so I'm going back now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3333337147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.0666670481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "もし良かったらなんだけど……\nfranさんがお暇なら、一緒にご飯に行かない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's okay with you…\nIf fran-san is free‚ would you like to go out for a dinner together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.0666670481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.3000003814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何よ急に。大損したばかりで出費も抑えたいのに\nあ、でも……遙子の奢りなら……考えなくもないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What is it all of a sudden? I just had a big expense and I don't have any money\nAh‚ but… if Haruko's paying for it… I might consider it",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3000003814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.5666670481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "来てくれるなら、もちろん全部奢るわよ！\nやったー！　ふふ、franさんとご飯楽しみだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you come with me‚ of course I'll pay for everything!\nYayー! Hehe‚ I'm looking forward to dinner with fran-san",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5666670481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.5666670481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふ、ちょうどチートデイだし\n好きなだけ食べてやろっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Fufu‚ it's a bit of cheat day‚ so\nI should eat as much as I want",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5666670481,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6699.9996186000035
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 85.0166670481
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "franさ～ん、もう一杯飲む～？\nねえねえねえ！　他のみんなも呼んじゃう～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san~‚ one more drink?\nHey‚ hey‚ hey! Shall I call other people?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666670481,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 91.4666670481
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 96.4000003814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁ、めんどくさ……そういえば遙子って\n酔っ払うとこんな感じなんだっけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ this is bothering me… now that I think about it‚ Haruko\nfeels like this when she's drunk…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4000003814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.6000003814
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "私の奢りなんだから、じゃんじゃん呼んで\nじゃんじゃん飲も～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm paying for everyone‚ more calling someone\nand more drink it~~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6000003814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 110.5000049591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "奢るって言っても、居酒屋じゃないの\nもっとオシャレな場所を期待してたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say I'm paying for everyone‚ it's an izakaya\nI was expecting a better place…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5000049591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 116.9333382924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……\nもう十分食べたし、どっかで切り上げないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…\nI've had enough‚ so I need to wrap it up somewhere…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.9333382924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 122.2333382924
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "もしもし、mihoさぁ～ん？\n今、franさんと飲んでるんだけどぉ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello‚ miho-san~?\nI'm drinking with fran-san right now~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.2333382924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 129.36668485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと！　何、電話掛けてるのよ！？\nそろそろ帰るわよ。お会計お願いね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait a minute! Why are you calling!?\nI'm going back soon. Please pay the bill!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.36668485,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17866.648483299996
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 135.4333413442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "え～～？　もう帰るのぉ～～？\nしょうがないなぁ……えっとぉ、お財布は～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh~~? Are you going back already~~?\nThere's nothing I can do… Um‚ where's my wallet…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4333413442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 149.6000080109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "あっれ～？　おかしいわね～\nfranさ～ん、お財布がかくれんぼしちゃったわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh~? That's weird~\nfran-san‚ my wallet's been playing hide-and-seek",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.6000080109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 161.4333413442
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "そんな訳ないでしょ\n……もしかして、どっか落としたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can't be\n…Did you drop it somewhere?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.4333413442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 168.1000080109
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03/sud_vo_adv_bond_hrk_01_03-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことは～……あ、寮に忘れてきちゃったかも！\nてへっ、遙子ってばドジなんだから～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not~… Ah‚ maybe I left it at the dorm!\nTehe‚ Haruko is such a klutz",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.1000080109,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 176.5333413442
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_pub-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "pub-00-night",
      "startTime": 180.9333332063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
